### Create manual flashcard
POST http://localhost:4321/api/flashcards
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{SUPABASE_JWT}}

{
  "front": "What is spaced repetition?",
  "back": "A learning technique that increases intervals between reviews."
}

### List flashcards (paginated)
GET http://localhost:4321/api/flashcards?limit=10&offset=0&order=created_at.desc
Authorization: Bearer {{SUPABASE_JWT}}

### Get single flashcard
GET http://localhost:4321/api/flashcards/{{CARD_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{SUPABASE_JWT}}

### Update flashcard content
PATCH http://localhost:4321/api/flashcards/{{CARD_ID}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{SUPABASE_JWT}}

{
  "front": "Define spaced repetition?"
}

### Soft delete flashcard
DELETE http://localhost:4321/api/flashcards/{{CARD_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{SUPABASE_JWT}}

### Batch save AI proposals (idempotent)
POST http://localhost:4321/api/flashcards/batch-save
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: {{REQUEST_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{SUPABASE_JWT}}

{
  "items": [
    { "front": "Q1", "back": "A1", "source": "ai" },
    { "front": "Q1", "back": "A1", "source": "ai" },
    { "front": "Q2", "back": "A2", "source": "ai_edited" }
  ]
}


